<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA20">
<l>kāṇap pukilaṟivu kaikkoṇṭa naṉṉeñca</l>
<l>nāṇap paṭumaṉṟē nāmpēciṉ māṇi</l>
<l>yuruvākik koṇṭulaka nīrēṟṟa cīrāṉ</l>
<l>ṟiruvākan tīṇṭiṟṟuc ceṉṟu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When we enter into envisaging, [our] good heart that has taken knowledge in hand</l>
<l>is ashamed, isn’t it, when we [even] speak – of going</l>
<l>[and] touching the sacred body of the excellent one</l>
<l>who accepted water for the earth, taking in in the form of a dwarf.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
